{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "qbczncm0ntk",
    "category": "movie",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qBczncM0ntk",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you so much for watching, and I'll see you in the next video, and I'll see you in the next video, and I'll see you in the next video.",
      "zh": "非常感謝您的觀看，我們下個影片見，我們下個影片見，我們下個影片見。",
      "ja": "ご視聴ありがとうございました。次のビデオでお会いしましょう。次のビデオでお会いしましょう。次のビデオでお会いしましょう。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll put a rush on those lab results, but my suspicion is that everything's fine.",
      "zh": "我會加快那些實驗室的結果，但我懷疑一切都沒問題。",
      "ja": "検査結果を急ぎますが、すべて問題ないと思います。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, thank you, Dr. Morgan. Thanks for seeing me.",
      "zh": "好的，謝謝你，摩根醫生。謝謝你見我。",
      "ja": "はい、ありがとう、モーガン医師。診てくれてありがとう。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Take care, no.",
      "zh": "保重，不。",
      "ja": "お大事に、いいえ。",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey.",
      "zh": "嘿。",
      "ja": "やあ。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What happened to your vacation?",
      "zh": "你的假期怎麼了？",
      "ja": "休暇はどうなったの？",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, leaving it 30 minutes.",
      "zh": "是的，只剩30分鐘。",
      "ja": "うん、あと30分で出発する。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sorry for calling you in, Addison.",
      "zh": "抱歉叫你來，艾迪生。",
      "ja": "呼び出してごめん、アディソン。",
      "time": "00:00:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Another emergency?",
      "zh": "又有緊急狀況？",
      "ja": "また緊急事態？",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Better now than after I leave.",
      "zh": "現在比我走後更好。",
      "ja": "私が去った後より今の方がいい。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You know we have an after-hour service that will refer them to another doctor, so you can actually go on vacation.",
      "zh": "你知道我們有下班後服務會轉介給其他醫生，所以你其實可以去度假。",
      "ja": "私たちには時間外サービスがあって、他の医者に紹介するから、実際に休暇に行けるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, I know.",
      "zh": "不，我知道。",
      "ja": "いいえ、知ってます。",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I have a sample in the back to send to the lab.",
      "zh": "喔，我後面有個樣本要送去實驗室。",
      "ja": "ああ、後ろに検体があって、検査室に送らなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Would you mind?",
      "zh": "你介意嗎？",
      "ja": "よろしいですか？",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll send it out.",
      "zh": "我會寄出去。",
      "ja": "私が送ります。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Rush on the results?",
      "zh": "加快結果？",
      "ja": "結果を急ぎますか？",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You know we will.",
      "zh": "你知道我們會的。",
      "ja": "もちろんそうしますよ。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Consider it then.",
      "zh": "那就當作已經加急了。",
      "ja": "そう考えてください。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, I'll take care of the rest of the paperwork and insurance.",
      "zh": "嘿，我會處理剩下的文書和保險。",
      "ja": "ねえ、残りの書類と保険は私がやるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You can move on.",
      "zh": "你可以繼續你的事。",
      "ja": "あなたは先に進んでいいよ。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, the best.",
      "zh": "嘿，最棒的。",
      "ja": "ねえ、最高だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sorry again for calling you in and interrupting your plans.",
      "zh": "再次抱歉叫你來打斷你的計劃。",
      "ja": "呼び出して計画を中断してごめんね。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, the only thing I have on my schedule today is lunch with my brother.",
      "zh": "嗯，我今天唯一的安排就是和我兄弟吃午餐。",
      "ja": "ええ、今日の予定は兄とランチだけです。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, enjoy that.",
      "zh": "那就好好享受吧。",
      "ja": "それを楽しんでね。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, be sure the lab knows how to reach me.",
      "zh": "喔，確保實驗室知道怎麼聯絡我。",
      "ja": "ああ、検査室が私に連絡できるようにしてね。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I've got it.",
      "zh": "我知道了。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have a good trip.",
      "zh": "旅途愉快。",
      "ja": "良い旅を。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "再見。",
      "ja": "さようなら。",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi, it's Addison Bert calling for my brother.",
      "zh": "嗨，我是艾迪生·伯特，想找我兄弟。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、アディソン・バートです。兄をお願いします。",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, he's been ignoring my texts.",
      "zh": "是的，他一直沒回我訊息。",
      "ja": "うん、彼は私のメッセージを無視している。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Could you remind him not to be late to lunch this time?",
      "zh": "你能提醒他這次不要遲到午餐嗎？",
      "ja": "今回はランチに遅れないように彼に伝えてくれますか？",
      "time": "00:01:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thanks so much.",
      "zh": "非常感謝。",
      "ja": "本当にありがとう。",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can you get these out?",
      "zh": "你能把這些拿出去嗎？",
      "ja": "これらを出してくれますか？",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We'll see a bunch of them.",
      "zh": "我們會看到很多。",
      "ja": "たくさん見ることになるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's tight, bud.",
      "zh": "很緊湊，夥計。",
      "ja": "きついよ、友よ。",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you?",
      "zh": "你是嗎？",
      "ja": "そうなの？",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Is that for him?",
      "zh": "那是給他的嗎？",
      "ja": "それは彼のため？",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yep.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have fun.",
      "zh": "玩得開心。",
      "ja": "楽しんでね。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will.",
      "zh": "我會的。",
      "ja": "そうするよ。",
      "time": "00:02:08"
    }
  ]
}